Glencore Increases Stake in South African Coal Producer Optimum to 25.8%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-08T11:57:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/glencore-increases-stake-in-south-african-coal-producer-optimum-to-25-8-.html
Glencore International Plc said it
raised its stake in South African coal producer  Optimum Coal
Holdings (OPT)  Ltd. to 25.8 percent from 24.7 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  